---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 290
  - Title: Ecclesiasticus
    Location: VI 35
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Orthodoxy-Ritual-Method=The Spiritual Master
---
Stand in the multitude of ancients that are wise, and join thyself
from thy heart to their wisdom, that thou mayst hear every discourse
of God, and the sayings of praise may not escape thee.
